Interface Replacer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Replacer
    Base interface for Replacer architecture.

    A Replacer's getReplacement method takes an object and replaces it by something else. Replacers with several arguments can be implemented using a BranchReplacer.

    Our replacers are usually created in ReplacerFactory and therefore have only default constructors.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andreas
